## Dart / Flutter Standards

- Files: `snake_case.dart` | Classes: `PascalCase` | Variables: `camelCase`
- Import order: Dart SDK > Flutter SDK > third-party > project (separated by blank lines)
- Always `const` constructors, trailing commas, `final` preference
- Never `print()` ‚Äî use `debugPrint()`
- Use `withValues(alpha: x)` not `withOpacity()`
- No `dynamic` without justification, no empty `catch` blocks
- No `setState` for business logic

---

## Multi-Theme Design (6 Themes)

Themes: nubar (default), dark, light, earth, ocean, amoled

- **NEVER** use `Colors.*` ‚Äî always `Theme.of(context).colorScheme.*`
- Cache at top of `build()`:
  ```dart
  final colorScheme = Theme.of(context).colorScheme;
  final textTheme = Theme.of(context).textTheme;
  ```
- Color mapping: `colorScheme.primary` (brand), `colorScheme.error` (not Colors.red), `colorScheme.surface` (not Colors.white), `colorScheme.onSurface.withValues(alpha: 0.6)` (muted text)
- Verify UI in at least nubar + dark themes

---

## Responsive Design

Breakpoints: mobile (<600px), tablet (600-1024px), desktop (>1024px)

- Never hardcode widths ‚Äî use `Flexible`, `Expanded`, `ConstrainedBox`
- Max content width on desktop: 800px, centered
- Use `MediaQuery.sizeOf(context)` for breakpoints
- Grid: 2 cols mobile, 3 tablet, 4 desktop
- Minimum touch target: 48x48
- Test at 360px, 768px, 1280px

---

## Localization (5 Languages)

Languages: ku (Kurmanji/LTR), ckb (Sorani/RTL), tr (Turkish/LTR), ar (Arabic/RTL), en (English/LTR)

- **NEVER** hardcode strings ‚Äî always `AppLocalizations.of(context)!.keyName`
- Update ALL 5 ARB files together; template: `app_ku.arb`
- Run `flutter gen-l10n` after changes
- Keys: `camelCase`, descriptive
- RTL: use `AlignmentDirectional`, `EdgeInsetsDirectional` (not `Alignment`, `EdgeInsets`)
- Test in both LTR and RTL

