## Feature Addition Checklist

1. Create `lib/features/<name>/{screens,providers,widgets,models}/`
2. Add l10n keys to ALL 5 ARB files
3. Run `flutter gen-l10n`
4. Create provider with `AsyncValue.guard()`
5. Create screen: `ConsumerWidget`, cache theme/l10n, use standard widgets
6. Test all 6 themes
7. Test RTL + LTR
8. Test responsive (mobile/tablet/desktop)
9. Add navigation route
10. If DB needed: migration + RLS + indexes

---

## Supabase Patterns

- Migrations: `NNN_description.sql`, immutable once committed
- RLS: enabled on all tables, SELECT by ownership/public, INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE scoped to owner
- Indexes on FK columns and `created_at DESC`
- Edge Functions: CORS headers + JWT verification + proper error responses
- UUIDs for PKs, `TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT NOW()` for timestamps

---

## Next.js SEO (next-seo/)

- Every page: `generateMetadata()` + JSON-LD + `generateStaticParams()`
- Open Graph + Twitter Card meta tags
- Never expose service role key to client
- Dynamic sitemap, proper robots.txt
- Kurdish keywords in meta, correct `lang`/`dir` attributes

---

## Widget & Screen Conventions

- Screens: `*Screen` suffix | Shared: `Nubar*` prefix | Feature: descriptive
- Use: `LoadingIndicator`, `NubarErrorWidget`, `NubarEmptyState`, `NubarAvatar`
- `CachedNetworkImage` (never `Image.network`), `PagedListView` (never load all)
- Handle all `AsyncValue` states: loading, error, data (with empty check)
